item.description:
I am currently a M.S. student majoring in Biostatistics and Data Science at Weill Cornell Medicine.

My interests lay in Data Science and I love dealing with data, especially investigating the intrinsic connection between variables by data wragling with dplyr and data visualization with the help of ggplot2. I have some hands on experience analyzing complex datasets using these packages and am looking foward to make more progress in the future!
